snippet.title: Kayak VR: Soča Valley DLC Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore the beautiful Soča Valley in Slovenia, known for its iconic green water, mountain vistas and lush nature. Take on a new thrilling challenge by paddling down whitewater rapids or explore the nature of this serene valley at your own pace.

Soča Valley is available right now as DLC on PS5 & PC:
PS5: https://store.playstation.com/product/EP7387-PPSA06948_00-DLCSOCA00PSAC200
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2926750
